#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:1619
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:1783
msgid "Exploring spatial relations"
msgstr "Istraživanje prostornih odnosa"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:3
msgid ""
"Geometric predicates are boolean functions used to determine the spatial "
"relation a feature has with another by comparing whether and how their "
"geometries share a portion of space."
msgstr ""
"Geometrijski predikati su logičke funkcije koje se koriste za utvrđivanje "
"prostornog odnosa jednog objekta prema drugom, poređenjem da li i kako "
"njihove geometrije dele deo prostora."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:10
msgid "Looking for spatial relations between layers"
msgstr "Traženje prostornih odnosa između slojeva"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:12
msgid ""
"Using the figure above, we are looking for the green circles by spatially "
"comparing them to the orange rectangle feature. Available geometric "
"predicates are:"
msgstr ""
"Na osnovu gornje slike, tražimo zelene krugove prostornim poređenjem sa "
"narandžastim pravougaonim objektom. Dostupni geometrijski predikati su:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:19
msgid "*Intersect*"
msgstr "*Preseca*"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:17
msgid ""
"Tests whether a geometry intersects another. Returns 1 (true) if the "
"geometries spatially intersect (share any portion of space - overlap or "
"touch) and 0 if they don’t. In the picture above, this will return circles "
"1, 2 and 3."
msgstr ""
"Proverava da li jedna geometrija preseca drugu. Vraća 1 (tačno) ako se "
"geometrije prostorno presecaju (dele bilo koji deo prostora - preklapaju se "
"ili dodiruju), a 0 ako se ne presecaju. Na gornjoj slici, ovo vraća krugove "
"1, 2 i 3."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:26
msgid "*Contain*"
msgstr "*Sadrži*"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:22
msgid ""
"Returns 1 (true) if and only if no points of b lie in the exterior of a, and"
" at least one point of the interior of b lies in the interior of a. In the "
"picture, no circle is returned, but the rectangle would be if you would look"
" for it the other way around, as it contains circle 1 completely. This is "
"the opposite of *are within*."
msgstr ""
"Vraća 1 (tačno) ako i samo ako nijedna tačka geometrije b ne leži izvan "
"geometrije a i bar jedna tačka unutrašnjosti geometrije b leži u "
"unutrašnjosti geometrije a. Na slici se ne vraća nijedan krug, ali bi se "
"vratio pravougaonik da tražite obrnuto, jer on u potpunosti sadrži krug 1. "
"Ovo je suprotno od *su unutar*."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:30
msgid "*Disjoint*"
msgstr "*Razdvojeno*"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:29
msgid ""
"Returns 1 (true) if the geometries do not share any portion of space (no "
"overlap, not touching). Only circle 4 is returned."
msgstr ""
"Vraća 1 (tačno) ako geometrije ne dele nijedan deo prostora (bez "
"preklapanja, bez dodirivanja). Vraća se samo krug 4."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:34
msgid "*Equal*"
msgstr "*Jednako*"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:33
msgid ""
"Returns 1 (true) if and only if geometries are exactly the same. No circles "
"will be returned."
msgstr ""
"Vraća 1 (tačno) ako i samo ako su geometrije potpuno iste. Neće se vratiti "
"nijedan krug."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:39
msgid "*Touch*"
msgstr "*Dodiruje*"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:37
msgid ""
"Tests whether a geometry touches another. Returns 1 (true) if the geometries"
" have at least one point in common, but their interiors do not intersect. "
"Only circle 3 is returned."
msgstr ""
"Proverava da li jedna geometrija dodiruje drugu. Vraća 1 (tačno) ako "
"geometrije imaju bar jednu zajedničku tačku, ali im se unutrašnjosti ne "
"presecaju. Vraća se samo krug 3."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:44
msgid "*Overlap*"
msgstr "*Preklapa*"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:42
msgid ""
"Tests whether a geometry overlaps another. Returns 1 (true) if the "
"geometries share space, are of the same dimension, but are not completely "
"contained by each other. Only circle 2 is returned."
msgstr ""
"Proverava da li se jedna geometrija preklapa sa drugom. Vraća 1 (tačno) ako "
"geometrije dele prostor, iste su dimenzije, ali nisu potpuno sadržane jedna "
"u drugoj. Vraća se samo krug 2."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:48
msgid "*Are within*"
msgstr "*Su unutar*"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:47
msgid ""
"Tests whether a geometry is within another. Returns 1 (true) if geometry a "
"is completely inside geometry b. Only circle 1 is returned."
msgstr ""
"Proverava da li je jedna geometrija unutar druge. Vraća 1 (tačno) ako je "
"geometrija a potpuno unutar geometrije b. Vraća se samo krug 1."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:56
msgid "*Cross*"
msgstr "*Ukršta*"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/algs_include.rst:51
msgid ""
"Returns 1 (true) if the supplied geometries have some, but not all, interior"
" points in common and the actual crossing is of a lower dimension than the "
"highest supplied geometry. For example, a line crossing a polygon will cross"
" as a line (true). Two lines crossing will cross as a point (true). Two "
"polygons cross as a polygon (false). In the picture, no circles will be "
"returned."
msgstr ""
"Vraća 1 (tačno) ako zadate geometrije imaju neke, ali ne sve, zajedničke "
"unutrašnje tačke i ako je samo ukrštanje niže dimenzije od najviše zadate "
"geometrije. Na primer, linija koja ukršta poligon ukršta ga kao linija "
"(tačno). Dve linije koje se ukrštaju ukrštaju se kao tačka (tačno). Dva "
"poligona ukrštaju se kao poligon (netačno). Na slici se neće vratiti nijedan"
" krug."

