#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:1917
msgid "Join attributes by nearest"
msgstr "Spajanje atributa po najbližem"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:1918
msgid ""
"Takes an input vector layer and creates a new vector layer with additional "
"fields in its attribute table. The additional attributes and their values "
"are taken from a second vector layer. Features are joined by finding the "
"closest features from each layer."
msgstr ""
"Uzima ulazni vektorski sloj i pravi novi vektorski sloj sa dodatnim poljima "
"u atributskoj tabeli. Dodatni atributi i njihove vrednosti preuzimaju se iz "
"drugog vektorskog sloja. Objekti se spajaju pronalaženjem najbližih objekata"
" iz svakog sloja."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:1924
msgid ""
"By default only the nearest feature is joined, but the join can also join to"
" the k-nearest neighboring features."
msgstr ""
"Podrazumevano se spaja samo najbliži objekat, ali spajanje može obuhvatiti i"
" k najbližih susednih objekata."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:1927
msgid ""
"If a maximum distance is specified, only features which are closer than this"
" distance will be matched."
msgstr ""
"Ako se zada najveće rastojanje, poklopiće se samo objekti koji su bliži od "
"tog rastojanja."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:1933
msgid ""
":ref:`qgisnearestneighbouranalysis`, :ref:`qgisjoinattributestable`, "
":ref:`qgisjoinattributesbylocation`, :ref:`qgisdistancematrix`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`qgisnearestneighbouranalysis`, :ref:`qgisjoinattributestable`, "
":ref:`qgisjoinattributesbylocation`, :ref:`qgisdistancematrix`"

