msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:joinbynearest``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:2052
msgid "Merge vector layers"
msgstr "Spajanje vektorskih slojeva"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:2053
msgid ""
"Combines multiple vector layers of the **same geometry** type into a single "
"one."
msgstr "Objedinjuje više vektorskih slojeva **iste geometrije** u jedan."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:2055
msgid ""
"The attribute table of the resulting layer will contain the fields from all "
"input layers. If fields with the same name but different types are found "
"then the exported field will be automatically converted into a string type "
"field. Optionally, new fields storing the original layer name and source can"
" be added."
msgstr ""
"Atributska tabela rezultujućeg sloja sadržaće polja iz svih ulaznih slojeva."
" Ako se pronađu polja istog naziva a različitog tipa, izvezeno polje biće "
"automatski pretvoreno u polje tipa niska. Opciono se mogu dodati nova polja "
"koja čuvaju naziv i izvor originalnog sloja."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:2060
msgid ""
"If any input layers contain Z or M values, then the output layer will also "
"contain these values. Similarly, if any of the input layers are multi-part, "
"the output layer will also be a multi-part layer."
msgstr ""
"Ako bilo koji ulazni sloj sadrži Z ili M vrednosti, izlazni sloj takođe će "
"ih sadržati. Slično, ako je bilo koji od ulaznih slojeva višedelni, i "
"izlazni sloj biće višedelni."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:2065
msgid ""
"Optionally, the destination coordinate reference system (CRS) for the merged"
" layer can be set. If it is not set, the CRS will be taken from the first "
"input layer. All layers will be reprojected to match this CRS."
msgstr ""
"Opciono se može postaviti odredišni koordinatni referentni sistem (CRS) "
"spojenog sloja. Ako se ne postavi, CRS se preuzima iz prvog ulaznog sloja. "
"Svi slojevi biće reprojektovani da odgovaraju tom CRS-u."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:2077
msgid ":ref:`qgissplitvectorlayer`"
msgstr ":ref:`qgissplitvectorlayer`"

