#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:2523
msgid ""
"Sets the encoding used for reading a layer's attributes. No permanent "
"changes are made to the layer, rather it affects only how the layer is read "
"during the current session."
msgstr ""
"Postavlja kodiranje koje se koristi za čitanje atributa sloja. Na sloju se "
"ne prave trajne izmene, već ovo utiče samo na to kako se sloj čita u tekućoj"
" sesiji."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:2527
msgid ""
"Changing the encoding is only supported for some vector layer data sources."
msgstr ""
"Promena kodiranja je podržana samo za neke izvore podataka vektorskih "
"slojeva."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:2544
