msgstr "**ID algoritma**: ``native:setlayerencoding``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:2580
msgid "Split features by character"
msgstr "Deljenje objekata po znaku"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:2581
msgid ""
"Features are split into multiple output features by splitting a field's "
"value at a specified character. For instance, if a layer contains features "
"with multiple comma separated values contained in a single field, this "
"algorithm can be used to split these values up across multiple output "
"features. Geometries and other attributes remain unchanged in the output. "
"Optionally, the separator string can be a regular expression for added "
"flexibility."
msgstr ""
"Objekti se dele na više izlaznih objekata deljenjem vrednosti polja na "
"zadatom znaku. Na primer, ako sloj sadrži objekte sa više vrednosti "
"razdvojenih zarezom u jednom polju, ovaj algoritam se može koristiti da se "
"te vrednosti razdvoje na više izlaznih objekata. Geometrije i ostali "
"atributi ostaju nepromenjeni u izlazu. Opciono, tekst razdvajača može biti "
"regularni izraz radi veće fleksibilnosti."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:2614
msgid "**Split using values in the field**"
msgstr "**Podeli koristeći vrednosti u polju**"

