msgid "Split vector layer"
msgstr "Deljenje vektorskog sloja"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:2670
msgid ""
"Creates a set of vectors in an output folder based on an input layer and an "
"attribute. The output folder will contain as many layers as the unique "
"values found in the desired field."
msgstr ""
"Pravi skup vektorskih slojeva u izlaznom folderu na osnovu ulaznog sloja i "
"atributa. Izlazni folder sadržaće onoliko slojeva koliko ima jedinstvenih "
"vrednosti u željenom polju."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:2675
msgid ""
"The number of files generated is equal to the number of different values "
"found for the specified attribute."
msgstr ""
"Broj generisanih datoteka jednak je broju različitih vrednosti pronađenih za"
" zadati atribut."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeneral.rst:2678
